org.efaps.jaas.xml

Class XMLPersonPrincipal

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.jaas.xml.AbstractXMLPrincipal
      • org.efaps.jaas.xml.XMLPersonPrincipal
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Principal

    public class XMLPersonPrincipal
extends AbstractXMLPrincipal
    The class implements the Principal interface for a person. The class is used from the XMLUserLoginModule class to implement a JAAS login module and set the person principals.
    A person principal instance stores also all found groups and roles.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    The eFaps Team
